Package: libtree-sitter-vim
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
Description: Vimscript grammar for tree-sitter
 tree-sitter-vim is a Vimscript grammar for tree-sitter. It enables syntax
 highlighting, structural editing, incremental parsing, and code analysis in
 editors and tools.
 .
 This package contains the shared library.

